title: 3 M7 Champs, who's next?
body:

replies.body: Do zed. I like how you place plat in there hahaha

if you want a challenge trust me zilean is a hard one to do. You can go 7/2/35 and that's not an S. You can go 2/0/14 and have 100% kill participation in a 20min game and that's still not an S. You can fucking have an afk mid and adc; you can carry and go 1/3/32 and that's still not an S (I think I can't remember it might have been an S actually).
